    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine dei eterni, breve ad memoriam habendam qualiter factum est
                        presentibus personis quas inferius nominabimus.
                                <persName><name>Ailina</name></persName> relicta quondam
                                <persName><name>Ierardini Mascarelli</name></persName>, propterea
                        quia cognovit plenam voluntatem suprascripti quondam viri sui Ierardini,
                        offerrendo beati <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs> qui vocatur <placeName
                                key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207">Teupasscio</placeName></orgName>
                        unam integram <rs key="#Petiae">petiam</rs> de terra cum multis arboribus et
                        omni hedificio super se habente que est posita in loco qui vocatur
                            <placeName key="#Petiae">Ultrario</placeName>, iuxta
                            <placeName>Filangnore</placeName>, que fuit recta et hedificata per
                        quondam massaium nomine <persName><name>Bernum</name></persName>. Postquam
                        predictus Ierardinus preocupatus fuit subitanea morte, tunc suprascripta
                        Ailina uxor in ipsa die obitus sui mariti, cum consilio et consensu
                                <persName><name>Formentini</name></persName> mundualdi sui et
                        aliorum multorum vicinorum parentum, pro remedio anime sue et suprascripti
                        Ierardini, per virgam quam in suas manibus tenebat, dedit et tradidit deo et
                        predicti <orgName key="#Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3209">hospitali et <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                                >ponti</rs> de Arno</orgName>, in manibus <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name>Iohanni</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Montanini</name></persName> in vice domini
                                <persName><name>Guidonis</name></persName> rectoris predicti
                        hospitali et ponti videlicet integram prenominatam petiam de terra cum
                        integriss omnibus arboribus super se et infra se habente (…).
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: argienti optimi sol. quatuor centum.
                            <foreign>Maledizioni</foreign>. Hoc factum est in loco qui vocatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/319">Cappiano</placeName>, in presentia et
                        testimonio <persName><name>Ubertinotti</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Vechii</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Henrichi</name></persName>, et
                                <persName><name>Forestani</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Ierardini</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Ugolinelli</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Grasi</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Gottifredi</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Brunonis</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guilgielmini</name></persName> filii quondam
                            <persName>Aldel(…)</persName> et
                            <persName><name>Arduini</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Guilgielmi</name></persName> et aliorum plurimum:
                                <persName><name>Borgongnonis</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name>Pungilion</name>(…)</persName>,
                                <persName><name>Maragonis</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Bernardini</name></persName> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Ficarelli</name></persName>, omnes predicti rogati
                            <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. Anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo quinquagesimo octavo, septimo kalendas iunii, indictione sexta.
                        (S) <persName><name>Hubertus</name></persName> donni inperatoris <rs
                            key="#Notary">notharius</rs> ibi fui et hoc breve scripsi. </ab>
